# gmail account
IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User alexander.matyasko@gmail.com
# PassCmd "pass show gmail.com"
PassCmd "echo ${PASSWORD:-$(copy_password.sh alexander.matyasko@gmail.com)}"
Port 993
SSLType IMAPS
AuthMechs Login
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Path ~/.mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/.mail/gmail/INBOX
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel gmail
Master :gmail-remote:
Slave :gmail-local:
# Patterns * ![Gmail]* "[Gmail]/Sent Mail" "[Gmail]/Starred" "[Gmail]/All Mail"
Patterns *
Create Slave
Sync All
Expunge Both
SyncState *

# ntu-student account
IMAPAccount student
Host localhost
Port 1143
User aliaksan001@e.ntu.edu.sg
PassCmd "echo ${PASSWORD:-$(copy_password.sh aliaksan001@e.ntu.edu.sg)}"
Timeout 1000
SSLType None
AuthMechs Login


IMAPStore student-remote
Account student

MaildirStore student-local
Path ~/.mail/student/
Inbox ~/.mail/student/INBOX
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel student
Master :student-remote:
Slave :student-local:
Patterns *
Create Slave
Sync All
Expunge Both
SyncState *

